+ Configure Flows\nfor Multiple Sources
++ Explicit Flows
+++_ CREATE FLOW ... AS INSERT INTO ... BY NAME
+++_ Multiple flows → single target table
+++_ No UNION required
++ Python Flows
+++_ @dp.append_flow(target="table")
+++_ Multiple decorators per target
+++_ Each source an independent flow
-- Benefits vs UNION
---_ Add new sources without modifying existing flows
---_ No full refresh triggered on changes
---_ More flexible and maintainable
-- Important Note
---_ Flow names identify checkpoints
---_ Renaming a flow resets its checkpoint
---_ Choose names carefully from the start
@endmindmap
